    "long_instructions": "Sanchit wants to create a \"dueling genres\" effect using the sample tracks:\r\n\r\n\"I want the beat and bass to sound like one genre for a bit, then I want it to switch to a different genre. Then that whole thing should repeat like they're clapping back at each other throughout the song\"\r\n\r\nCan you help Sanchit create this song? Use the example below to hear what this could sound like!\r\n\r\n**Specific Requirement:** Your song should use a nested loop!\r\n\r\n\r\n<details>\r\n  <summary>Validation Details</summary>\r\n  <table>\r\n  <tr style=\"border: 1px solid black; padding: 1px\">\r\n\t  <td>Condition</td>\r\n\t  <td>S/F?</td>\r\n\t  <td>Message</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr style=\"border: 1px solid black; padding: 1px\">\r\n\t  <td>Uses a nested loop</td>\r\n\t  <td>S</td>\r\n\t  <td>Great job!</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr style=\"border: 1px solid black; padding: 1px\">\r\n\t  <td>Uses at least 1 loop (but not a nested loop)</td>\r\n\t  <td>F</td>\r\n\t  <td>You'll need a nested loop to make the pattern repeat!</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr style=\"border: 1px solid black; padding: 1px\">\r\n\t  <td>No loops</td>\r\n\t  <td>F</td>\r\n\t  <td>Make sure to use a loop to make your tracks repeat at least once!</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n</details>",
